summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Walleta Finnish personal finance management app. Backend APIs working perfectly (100% success rate), frontend UI loading correctly with Finnish text, user registration/login flows working, navigation between all pages successful, and core CRUD operations functional.

design_issues.issue: Logout button location unclear in UI - could not locate logout option in user menu

User registration flow works - can create account with email/password
User login flow works - can login with registered credentials
Dashboard loads after login and shows overview with Finnish text
Navigation between all pages works (expenses, incomes, budget, loans, savings)
All backend API endpoints working (26/26 tests passed)
CRUD operations for savings goals working
Dashboard summary endpoint providing correct data
Finnish language text displaying correctly throughout app
Responsive design elements working on desktop viewport
